data.title: Astrology Birth Chart for Rachèl Louise (Jul. 8, 1989)
data.meta_description: Liz has two passions in life: astrology and relationships. As a professional astrologer, she has been featured in multiple publications such as BestLife, FoxNews, Glam, Glamour, and MindBodyGreen. She shares all her discoveries and observations on this website.
data.text:
Rachèl Louise is a Dutch-American singer-songwriter. After winning the Utrechtse Popprijs in 2011 and being called Serious Talent at the Dutch pop/rock radio station 3FM, she released her debut album Be Your Own Cheerleader on October 5, 2012.

Rachèl Louise was born on July 8, 1989, in Utrecht, Utrecht, The Netherlands. Her birth geographical coordinates are 52° 5’ 27” North latitude and 5° 7’ 20” East longitude. Rachèl Louise is currently 35 years old.

Astrologically, Rachèl Louise falls under the Sun sign of Cancer, with Virgo as her Ascendant, Virgo as her Moon sign, and Libra as her Black Moon Lilith sign.
